Package: ydisctools
Type: Package
Title: Your CDISC Related Tools
Version: 0.0.236
Author: Yoichi Masui
Maintainer: Yoichi Masui <masui.yoichi@gmail.com>
Description: A collection of small, focused tools for CDISC programming
    (SDTM, ADaM and TFL), including dataset builders, Define-XML /
    Pinnacle 21 metadata readers, ISO 8601 date helpers, controlled
    terminology lookups, byte-aware text splitting, and a Sankey
    treatment-flow plotter. RTF table generation functions are based on
    the r2rtf package (Wang et al., 2020).
License: GPL (>= 3)
URL: https://ichirio.github.io/ydisctools/, https://github.com/ichirio/ydisctools
BugReports: https://github.com/ichirio/ydisctools/issues
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
RoxygenNote: 7.3.2
Roxygen: list(markdown = TRUE)
Depends:
    R (>= 4.1.0)
Suggests:
